    "It is up to the user of the service whether the generated content (output) is exploited in any way and how.",
    "Four issues must be addressed in the contractual liability for output: liability for its use (a), liability disclaimers (b), limitation of liability (c) and circumventing any potential sole liability of the initial developer of a GenAI for its output (d).",
